 <h2>Further Hunting in Paludal Caverns</h2><br><br><br>Paludal is an insanely good exp zone for lower levels. Especially for Mages, as we can solo well here. As a Mage you should never take a bandits group, its just not worth it exp wise.<br><br>Soloing is the way, or duo or similar with another high dps class. There are a few great spots in this zone, coming out from ShadowHaven you will pass a lone shroom spawn, this is a fantastic camp, alternatively invis and head down and right, through the bandits, and you will see a ramp covered in fiends. These are great to solo, just DS and Burnout pet and send it in, then either heal or nuke. If your pet gets hit with their DoT the low level pet heal will remove it as well as restoring hp.<br><br><br>Happy hunting.<br><br><br><br></center><b><u>Comments/Feedback:</u></b><br><br>
